        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "80dcef19-d52e-4c32-be9e-65bb3c0e3701",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "41b028bb-f983-4b0f-bfd0-086d246ac2d7",
      "type": "h2",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "1. Purpose"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6a76c-e99c-4c84-9e37-f5803663148a",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "To establish procedures for calibrating laboratory equipment to ensure accurate and reliable results. Proper calibration guarantees that instruments function within specified tolerances and meet the quality and regulatory requirements of the laboratory."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "353af0fc-79d4-4d8b-b1f9-2e00ec9bde87",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "c3d05946-af06-4a87-9d71-6546caa29601",
      "type": "h2",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "2. Scope"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "e48032d0-66f6-452a-a0f8-d7b9fce1283a",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "This SOP applies to all laboratory personnel responsible for the use, calibration, and maintenance of laboratory instruments. It covers the calibration procedures for various types of equipment, including balances, pH meters, spectrophotometers, centrifuges, thermometers, and pipettes."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "f6b974a6-e08b-461e-9dd5-8df402b9448e",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "2c60da51-d7da-4c41-ae9f-565f2ed60ccf",
      "type": "h2",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "3. Responsibilities"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "e67a0827-7dcc-4176-b9b8-aabb00c8c3d3",
      "type": "h2",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "6057a9a5-a79f-4a1a-82ad-de38864639be",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Lab Manager"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "f97e1de6-b0b8-43aa-ac72-81121a23aa0d",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "e44000ff-52dc-46e9-a69d-a63fdbb325fd",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Ensures that all laboratory equipment is calibrated according to the calibration schedule."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "9b0f5eff-50bc-462d-9db0-9fcf0436ea06",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "d58b934b-ff4d-450b-8473-a5c489e90da2",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Maintains calibration records."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "2cc6a2f7-2400-4f8a-8d4d-88fa23f479ab",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Lab Personnel"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "c216a87d-80e9-4c32-a350-e75ceaae7c6d",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "f5e0b7f1-b1f5-471e-a67a-5b39d74d1e11",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Performs equipment calibration according to this SOP."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "53ff9dab-70b7-4002-997e-00073731f318",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "85b596a6-a2f1-4050-940b-5ff025792a2a",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Documents calibration results in the Calibration Log."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "0e9ca5cd-2e4d-4c68-91d1-328f2be496dc",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Quality Assurance Officer"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "1ec98f3d-8d8d-4862-8000-d1fcacfe7950",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "a7eb41ef-68c1-47a6-be89-481b9d74aa07",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Audits calibration records periodically."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "90f028e4-6a53-497c-bb7e-4457f2919d23",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "6d208b13-034f-498f-9bc7-380bdf716fbc",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Ensures compliance with calibration standards."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "c989a12f-3d5c-42b4-9fe2-f3aa494f5d2e",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "512d41ce-ab7a-4909-8cf5-0d8560f5b7f2",
      "type": "h2",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "4. Definitions"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "8f25f70b-9622-4861-a1ae-17a9b7d77115",
      "type": "h2",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "92f57ca5-1702-41dc-94f1-3bc81bc77ea9",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Calibration"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "09c754d6-2577-4198-86bb-9d118b283022",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "The process of comparing the output of an instrument to a known standard to ensure accuracy."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "2fde3ba1-0094-4463-ae1f-5e481774e469",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Standard"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "eaabd895-9a55-4478-80a6-8f0ebc541984",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "A known reference material or tool used during calibration to ensure accuracy and precision."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "82f10754-c8ee-4fff-887e-13e31724e4be",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Tolerance"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "5381d95e-431d-4478-b64f-192e5acd1884",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "The acceptable range of variation from the true value that an instrument may have during operation."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "157a6748-6f7f-4a9d-b81d-0cc75bdd83b8",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "18663152-97a8-4663-b1ff-0bcc17687e6a",
      "type": "h2",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "5. Calibration Procedures"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "8c78f08d-e02d-4abc-abe9-66908c5c1de9",
      "type": "h2",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "daf54d1f-fb80-41d7-82ee-c4806ea7ebd6",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "5.1 General Calibration Guidelines"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "960f9f75-a692-471b-a936-d6d45fffc525",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Frequency of Calibration"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "8134bf58-dd7f-4c25-bdba-d37d65e01331",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "f38b8a92-ff58-417a-9566-eb91d37d20b3",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "All instruments must be calibrated as per manufacturer recommendations or at regular intervals specified in this SOP (e.g., daily, monthly, quarterly, annually)."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "827b37ea-4fe5-4ced-bf39-a48d9c4e42ba",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "9e289b16-7db4-4a7d-85e4-1ee75ea5b250",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Critical instruments require more frequent calibration."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "222ca9ba-92c3-4f29-82fb-f86deb07e6a6",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Pre-Calibration Checks"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "042f4db8-185e-4f93-95b6-d59ea443f2a7",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "6c1cc5f5-d532-43cf-99a1-715a1036dfe8",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Ensure the instrument is clean, functional, and has been warmed up according to the manufacturer’s instructions."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "80456b2a-8cb4-40c0-b35a-73fa3b342ed2",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "354a47fa-b2e4-4d13-a855-cf5040f4bc27",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Inspect calibration standards to ensure they are in good condition and within expiry."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "9f0d3e11-6739-4de8-b88b-977adbafbd50",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Documentation"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ef610040-dec1-495e-ae42-84136989e791",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "63f880c1-f7de-4df9-bb9d-991c558fa53a",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Record calibration activities in the Calibration Log, including:"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "2869ef5c-2043-4cca-a005-589fb2a9a5de",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 1,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "fb9770be-d315-4d32-8581-e53567ed4777",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Date of calibration"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "dd3347f9-26cb-4cc3-b26b-36d653bb5d57",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 1,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "a10173ae-a8b2-44ef-ac41-c015354f1fee",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Calibration results"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "62c3dd21-f23b-42ae-95a8-25043855a068",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 1,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "04e0e02e-b79c-4a40-ba20-2d6c89edda23",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Instrument model and serial number"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "68b3fa44-8707-4c11-9021-0df6d5a00807",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 1,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "c22b170a-5a22-4b33-abf4-feac7fd476a3",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Calibration standard used"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "d30a45c4-86c3-4eff-80bf-57929aab824d",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 1,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "e9937269-c5f3-4b5e-b463-1c1d1163d1bc",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Person performing the calibration"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "d688d49d-0a4b-453d-a677-51a7d30ca796",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "84b5ce16-305b-41e5-a6ea-dfd99f4b0da2",
      "type": "h2",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "6. Instrument-Specific Calibration Procedures"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "eba238e8-866e-48cd-b375-6df80fab0d1e",
      "type": "h2",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "2bfaaf09-c0c8-4f67-9aca-091485dcee10",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "6.1 Balance Calibration"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "bc8e4ca4-8500-4829-9c5b-baf2f08e55ce",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Frequency:"
        },
        {
          "text": " Daily before use or upon relocation."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "fac19adf-2a97-44f5-bf71-df7c042a3062",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Procedure:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "21cfe44c-3b17-4f77-b121-026fbb6745aa",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "ee0e35f9-cdf1-411c-9342-5f8a39042263",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Turn on the balance and allow it to warm up."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "b0a0b63d-595d-4bb0-b253-a6c29c338cc0",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "58dbc90b-d4ca-47d1-bfdb-4e1f5c8dbc16",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Zero the balance."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "76157287-d1fe-4b16-bb43-df36c112b530",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "05ce00f9-773a-4328-bdc2-6f7ec2decd44",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Place certified weights (e.g., 1g, 10g, 100g) and record displayed values."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "5fd97d17-83df-4b2c-807f-9b3bea2dcc77",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "9bbf7969-98a1-4c20-8a92-20eeb125d11f",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Compare displayed values with certified weights:"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "2743c373-9643-47ba-8e58-a7ff57460cb6",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 1,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "d53ad1e0-9449-44db-9138-7411f71b2c4a",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Adjust or recalibrate if values fall outside tolerance (±0.001g for analytical balances)."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ead4a727-8519-4f22-b335-02793c9fa85c",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "dc14132a-f91e-4983-9df8-239c59300931",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Document results in the Calibration Log."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "a3cf8798-e5d5-42de-bad5-5610beaa6c5a",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "fad363cf-e468-4dbf-811c-44404c98a7b2",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "6.2 pH Meter Calibration"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "82ce4a65-892e-463e-ad42-6b537692194f",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Frequency:"
        },
        {
          "text": " Before each use or daily for frequent use."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "594db4b7-fbfe-43aa-b6ea-1e784bdc992a",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Procedure:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "b86a0e6b-2618-4368-8152-dd9e5ffdd857",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "71240f51-8068-48be-a158-842c51d738ac",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Prepare fresh buffer solutions (pH 4.00, 7.00, and 10.00)."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "4530a572-4d00-497d-82d1-0d7ac4adb05b",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "a7c6b304-c921-400e-b67f-f1371b33ad8a",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Rinse the electrode with deionised water and blot dry."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "6c8341da-78f6-4ebd-a6ee-4326d0d6701d",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "17c5c6b1-b611-4178-a206-d5ec5a7689b3",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Immerse the electrode in pH 7.00 buffer; adjust the meter to 7.00."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "daf839b7-31d8-4c62-bfa1-bb4f3379de51",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "e19e31a7-c446-4cff-8e49-5770cc003bb4",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Repeat with pH 4.00 and pH 10.00 buffers, adjusting as necessary."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "815dfef6-3c32-4ac7-98db-498a2b1f28c3",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "6b995bd6-aadb-42d2-b9c5-da9bea10572c",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Rinse the electrode between measurements."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "fcbe324d-1f7e-4775-8294-ae47fa21ff03",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "e2b3a40e-cc91-42a8-a247-6988b8da0843",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Document results in the Calibration Log."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "641e719a-6a2b-44a5-bdfa-35af0ae30b51",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "52034db7-a17f-4b8c-9e98-fefdda41565c",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "6.3 Spectrophotometer Calibration"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "84642783-fdac-44ff-b138-4be59ba35691",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Frequency:"
        },
        {
          "text": " Monthly or before critical measurements."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "31231420-7075-4846-a272-10a59141571a",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Procedure:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "8c33026d-104e-44df-91eb-4c20d58a7dae",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "95f85780-faf4-421d-9d2e-fe7f4062bd82",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Warm up the spectrophotometer."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "b25f93a1-a475-43cd-a2fe-7af5f76c55d7",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "1b95e0e4-f30e-4c44-97f1-7ab4288855d9",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Set the wavelength range as required."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "34474613-1982-4ecb-bac7-00fdd1129b97",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "d6a98aa4-d479-4ecf-b076-edc45f44fb46",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Insert a blank solution and zero the absorbance."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "c657d097-4067-42f1-aca1-a4e5d19797ad",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "36473b41-c4ac-4930-aa95-e5f786ab0a66",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Test a standard solution with known absorbance."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "e684d106-9f45-4a15-908a-dc32b3b0ac5b",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "d6c7e995-f88c-4f84-9e58-4371815f7c75",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Compare measured values with expected values:"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "e0ce91e7-d365-4242-8826-c0f15bdf3dc6",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 1,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "6bfdc603-ce96-4333-9e8a-621fed73d88d",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Adjust or troubleshoot if readings fall outside tolerance (±0.005 absorbance units)."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "7fcfb8da-02f9-441b-b1ea-541e02e196bc",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "b99f9079-0fbc-4e6b-97df-51f283a6f6fc",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Document results in the Calibration Log."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "991d8e24-a546-47e1-b957-bf5a5ea003c4",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "cda89bab-e236-418d-8a0d-2c5394bf224f",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "6.4 Centrifuge Calibration"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "35b8e955-0b2b-4225-b72e-7d7a6c605053",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Frequency:"
        },
        {
          "text": " Annually or after repair/maintenance."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ef80b633-4e05-4a2d-a976-d530684f85e8",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Procedure:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "a9a661cb-17e8-4310-b4ee-28e2aaa30a03",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "3febd897-e0ba-4abe-bd4d-dcb512f2f67a",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Clean and balance the centrifuge."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "6d4fc3db-abf6-4a5c-bb28-2172094a958c",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "9ce8c555-8f60-4d29-9a77-37d835265f91",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Measure speed with a calibrated tachometer."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "82145ecc-b858-4ad7-8a2a-5c78c8fac579",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "9f603070-25f3-40ed-8857-44ec487ce9d5",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Run the centrifuge at a specified speed (e.g., 5000 RPM) and record the tachometer reading."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "622a4b49-b235-4798-965d-fbd3a6811a3e",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "780f4e08-6b8d-48ec-bd46-170a55dd2664",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Adjust if the actual RPM deviates from the set RPM (±5% tolerance)."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "71c80a5d-372e-4c31-9dec-133ba452310b",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "8222094e-a696-4f28-b6cb-510b86c5b6e6",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Document results in the Calibration Log."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "7a736b6d-92e1-4b9e-ac9e-d2cf2c2a130d",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "6f7f51ea-bad8-4cdd-bb24-bd92fe47466b",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "6.5 Pipette Calibration"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "fe8417a6-4542-4ad7-9316-869f4631e2e1",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Frequency:"
        },
        {
          "text": " Quarterly or after repairs."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "4e7663b7-c913-41b2-ba7c-b8a24d0648d5",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "Procedure:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "1f3bb970-0e6e-4f81-bb36-dbfabcd30dc5",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "69496313-c9f6-4cdd-8fa5-3e0fef631c1c",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Select test volumes (e.g., 10µL, 100µL, 1000µL)."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "4e844ac4-7b8d-4db7-b892-364b524c0a19",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "c15610d7-547b-4ed4-a594-d45779555946",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Weigh the dispensed liquid on a calibrated balance."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "4d68d13a-563f-4f35-a490-52d571d5bcef",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "a20412d9-4373-4819-8ecc-ebc86fe399f6",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Convert weight to volume using water’s density (1g = 1mL)."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "aa52eee8-8e22-4cff-91d1-5c20ec2eb574",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "0c969291-41e1-4eab-bd53-1cfdc2057cfe",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Compare measured volumes with expected values:"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "43af4581-1b8e-4bd3-9094-f0e3850cfa1a",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 1,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "b989906c-faf0-4aad-b6ca-11453077577e",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Adjust if values fall outside tolerances (±1% for ≥10µL; ±5% for <10µL)."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "d729a679-265b-4a7e-8a55-be923d3975ff",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "b88e37bb-f2f6-494d-a198-85f2b89bec8a",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Document results in the Calibration Log."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "daf1516d-9f3b-45f0-a0e1-14654277d4a7",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "02097110-0ff3-499d-bb4b-436a88c5c983",
      "type": "h2",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "7. Calibration Failure and Corrective Actions"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "da718f41-7538-4b50-a421-3efe7e6f584e",
      "type": "h2",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "bd9e06c4-2313-4cc3-88fc-fa7edc122c35",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "7.1 Deviation from Calibration Standards"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "d77d77e3-2a4e-4a7b-9601-7c079f28c305",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "bfd34b31-fc82-4b76-902e-d2ecd191bcb4",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Recalibrate if initial calibration fails."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "3cd84946-4aff-4205-bf98-0bd8ce60d064",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "af5b2125-9ea0-4490-a279-b0f9a4770f6e",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "If recalibration fails, tag the instrument as \"Out of Calibration\" and notify the Lab Manager."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "18cacc72-243d-47ef-a3b9-3a03e458f65b",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "1fc83b83-11f1-4609-965b-21a7babe9465",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Arrange for repair or replacement."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "dd4a4b23-585f-43d2-bbd8-e34f44715568",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "557cc49f-fef2-482f-b3f4-808c7f96687b",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "7.2 Revalidation"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "eb500e49-50e3-4c69-840e-28f18525b002",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "8710ebdc-6891-49e4-a301-245c1dd50247",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "After repair or recalibration, validate the instrument by performing a full calibration test."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "701ac762-65c9-4f4b-ad06-a1172ffe6115",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "243101bf-692a-4265-95b9-ebbaf65cf145",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Confirm results meet tolerances before returning the instrument to use."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "6c7b7e81-aa05-47e5-94d7-bcc68751b308",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "0669f3a5-fbe6-4160-b54b-a3529b7f56a0",
      "type": "h2",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "8. Record-Keeping and Documentation"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "58514332-b2b5-44c3-8750-7d6f86013f67",
      "type": "h2",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "42fc1bee-3ef7-4604-a253-8dc0b866691c",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "8.1 Calibration Log"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "868341e5-1e82-4be5-9bc4-8b5f3cd267e2",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "e476d4bf-f1b7-48d9-ae54-634b9d833152",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Maintain a Calibration Log for each instrument, including:"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "4a769f70-82c3-4c6d-85d7-5a6ca09c46cd",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 1,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "ca5fe588-42fc-4809-974d-f116e974fb91",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Instrument name, model, and serial number"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "3b90d550-8d89-4092-b4da-46c1e8f8ed50",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 1,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "eb9b9b50-339b-49b0-9076-74527523f086",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Date of calibration"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "c67a597c-eecc-4807-8c07-e1305b9fe81a",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 1,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "ad861f64-ce19-47d4-ad10-adceaa6a6401",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Calibration results and deviations"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "984e1da7-fd50-4be7-b915-a010585a7606",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 1,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "5b29e4a6-be62-4bcb-b780-70403128cdd1",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Name of the person performing calibration"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "61617367-93ce-4a4e-9325-a88e647ab162",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 1,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "3294b18f-8058-476c-b438-06e39aa5c3e4",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Next scheduled calibration date"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "d70f5118-41ee-4699-ba96-4cad187b19d1",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "d214e96c-36bc-42c8-81b4-916b9314d069",
      "type": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "8.2 Calibration Certificates"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "5066886e-35b2-41d9-bf89-c1b3b7b453d0",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "8257bc88-3b3a-4dde-945c-606298e7c59b",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Obtain calibration certificates for equipment calibrated by external vendors and store them with equipment documentation."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "daa9a6ec-a29c-48fb-929e-602baadb74a6",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "a0b5aca5-35b3-4f42-8782-801a342f2067",
      "type": "h2",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "9. Training"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "694e62be-898e-4eda-84e6-5aea1313c682",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "4958ead0-0665-4cd2-90e8-af07ba706a0a",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "All personnel involved in calibration must receive training on relevant equipment."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "22b1cf70-1f6d-4e36-a3da-90d9f74042ee",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "09a921a4-80c6-4776-876f-8acef419051e",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Provide annual refresher training or when new equipment is introduced."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "12c908cd-418d-458e-a1fe-41ab607da77a",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "74c24426-e1ab-43b4-b336-4ed0d46f30e1",
      "type": "h2",
      "children": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "text": "10. References"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "e49c4b09-9a76-4b3f-8b5a-244d88ac045c",
      "type": "li",
      "indent": 0,
      "children": [
        {
          "id": "a39e3192-20c3-41a4-9052-b9eef5f2d7a8",
          "type": "lic",
          "children": [
